DESCRIPTION:Join us for Tree and People Coalitions’ Canopy Awards! \\nCeleb
	rating works of architects\\\, landscape designers\\\, developers\\\, urba
	n planners\\\, community organizations and educators within the greater Se
	attle metropolitan area that:\\n• Demonstrate an outstanding commitment to
	 the preservation and planting of urban trees\\n• Thoughtfully integrate b
	uildings within their existing site context and environmental conditions\\
	n• Develop educational programs that enrich and engage the community\\\, w
	ith a primary emphasis on creating healthy urban environments. \\nOpen to 
	ages 12+. Children ages 12-17 must be accompanied by a guardian. No pets. 
	No outside food or beverages – venue refreshments only. \\nRegister \\nLea
	rn more about Trees and People Coalition here.\n\nhttps://www.seattleparks
