DTSTAMP:20260315T214150Z
DTSTART:20260411T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Spring Restoration Day is back! \\nJoin your friends and neighb
	ors for this extended version of Volunteer Park Trust’s 2nd Saturday work 
	party! We’ll be mulching\\\, weeding\\\, and maybe even planting a larger 
	area within the park for this event to beautify Volunteer Park for everyon
	e to enjoy. This is a great event for kids and families.  \\nMeet us at th
	e Black Sun Sculpture across from Seattle Asian Art Museum at 10:00 AM on 
	Saturday. If you arrive late\\\, look for our green signboard telling you 
	where in the park we will be working. \\nWe will provide the gloves and to
	ols. \\nRegister \\nLearn more about Volunteer Park Trust here.\n\nhttps:/
	/www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/volunteer-park-2nd-saturday-work-par
	ty-3/\n\nFrom The Seattle Parks Foundation
